            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the<strong> drained potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a small splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth – this is your <strong>mash</strong></p>",
