    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pie is almost done, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced carrot</strong> and cook for an initial 5-6 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>After 5-6 min, add the <strong>shredded kale </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 3-4 min further or until tender with a bite – this is your <strong>garlicky veg</strong></p>",
